title: Kadhal
subTitle: Aishwarya, a young student from a wealthy family, falls in love with Murugan, a scooter mechanic. She convinces him to elope with her, but things take a drastic turn when her family tracks them down.

title: Kaadhal Solla Vandhen
subTitle: Prabhu, a fresher in college, falls in love with Sandhya, his senior. However, this does not go well with her classmates and they start to create problems for him.

title: Teleshopping
subTitle: Learn about a wide selection of products and take advantage of a convenient method of shopping. A show for those who love to shop from the comforts of their home.

subTitle: In order to impress Shakthi, Bruce Lee wears a superhero costume and performs martial arts techniques. However, he gets involved in a police chase and helps the officers seize the offenders.

subTitle: Janaki and Krishna fall in love, unaware of the estranged relationship between their fathers. Later, they strive to convince their families to approve their relationship.

subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Tamilselvanum Thaniyar Anjalum
